1
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:08,239
This Mao City is pretty lively.

2
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:09,239
Hey, hey!

3
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:09,719
Sir!

4
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,159
Come check out our Tianxiang Pavilion.

5
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,519
Your second girl is half price!

6
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:13,560
Also,

7
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,480
get this stamp,

8
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:16,599
and watch the rock-smashing show for free.

9
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,599
These are Zhang Fei eyebrows, imported from the West.

10
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,840
It's all the rage!

11
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,920
Chicken's Here Hotpot Shop!

12
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,959
We sell a hundred chickens every day,

13
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:22,159
never kept overnight!

14
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:25,040
Everything's just two coins!

15
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,000
What kind of weather is this?

16
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,400
Pouring down out of nowhere!

17
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:36,400
Alright.

18
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,280
Next!

19
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,920
Hey.

20
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,319
I want to see Prince Mao.

21
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,159
Sorry, sorry.

22
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,079
She's got a screw loose.

23
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:48,920
I can't control her either.

24
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:49,680
Sorry, sorry.

25
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,840
Actually, we barely know each other.

26
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,200
Sorry, sorry.

27
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,040
Everyone, please wait a bit longer.

28
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,120
Just a little while longer.

29
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,359
Truly sorry.

30
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,200
If you don't have an appointment,

31
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:05,239
Prince Mao won't be free until next March.

32
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:05,480
What?

33
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:09,000
No time to see me, yet you want me to fill out forms?

34
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,240
I'll trash this whole palace, you wanna bet?

35
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,680
And sell you off to a brothel!

36
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,120
So sorry.

37
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,080
Well, since he's busy,

38
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,919
we'll be on our way.

39
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:16,479
See you around.

40
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,000
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

41
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,520
He just said he has no time.

42
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,120
Let's go find another prince.

43
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,400
Don't you have an imperial court token?

44
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,879
Show it to her.

45
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,639
I hate people who pull rank like you.

46
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:27,800
Will flashing the token even work?

47
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,159
Miss.

48
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,000
Oh.

49
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,800
You two are from the imperial court?

50
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,159
That's right.

51
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,840
Why didn't you say so sooner?

52
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,759
Prince Mao has long held a grudge against the Emperor.

53
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,319
So court officials get absolutely no special treatment.

54
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:45,520
Come back in March, the year after next.

55
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:49,840
Listen here.

56
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:53,039
I'm your future Princess Consort.

57
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:56,039
Crossing me will not end well for you.

58
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,360
Sorry.

59
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:00,000
Prince Mao's concubine quota is full.

60
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,199
If you'd like to be a maidservant,

61
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,879
please fill out a form first.

62
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,599
Every year on November 11th,

63
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,039
along with 200 other candidates,

64
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,960
you'll take a standardized exam together.

65
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,120
Maidservant?

66
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,039
Exam?

67
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:17,759
Just who do you think I am?

68
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,039
Are you a barbarian?

69
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,000
Hitting people at the drop of a hat.

70
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,439
Next time you try any tricks on me,

71
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:24,960
just you try.

72
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,039
Hey, hey, hey.

73
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,360
Hey, buddy.

74
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:29,319
Need a queue number?

75
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,719
All freshly stolen numbers.

76
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,520
Dates guaranteed fresh.

77
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,280
No thanks.

78
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:33,960
How much?

79
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,199
A hundred taels.

80
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,639
There are so many princes out there,

81
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,000
why hang yourself on just one tree?

82
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,319
Can't we try a few other princes?

83
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,199
Will it be silver notes or cash?

84
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:43,680
When I was eight,

85
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:47,319
I just sold a few things to the maids and eunuchs.

86
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,280
Just a little side hustle.

87
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,639
And Father banished me from the palace.

88
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:53,080
Now you finally come crawling back to beg me.

89
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:56,120
So, are you going to be Emperor or not?

90
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:00,639
Originally, becoming Emperor

91
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,960
did tempt me just a little bit.

92
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,680
But someone told me

93
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,879
that being Emperor

94
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:07,000
means no freedom,

95
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:09,000
and no personal space.

96
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:09,800
That's true.

97
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,159
Then we'll take our leave.

98
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,120
Once you're Emperor,

99
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,759
all the treasures of Great Liang

100
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,160
will be yours.

101
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,199
Treasures?

102
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,959
Once you're Emperor,

103
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:27,120
everyone in Great Liang will worship you.

104
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,160
Worship?

105
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:36,399
Prince Mao, Prince Mao!

106
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,120
I'm right here.

107
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,759
Look over here!

108
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,959
Once you're Emperor,

109
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,800
besides the 3,000 beauties of the harem,

110
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,399
you can also marry someone like me,

111
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:47,040
a gentle and beautiful princess.

112
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,879
A gentle, beautiful princess?

113
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:53,800
Forget it.

114
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:55,360
You two should leave for now.

115
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,720
I need to catch up with my buddy here.

116
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,079
Buddy?

117
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,240
It's you.

118
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,480
Don't tell me you're that "buddy."

119
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,160
Sorry,

120
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,319
beat you to it.

121
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:14,959
Guards!

122
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,399
Show him out.

123
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,199
Hey!

124
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,439
Wait a minute!

125
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:19,680
I can't give up.

126
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,240
I've said all there is to say.

127
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,480
He simply refuses to be Emperor.

128
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:23,040
No way!

129
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,319
Ouch!

130
00:05:29,399 --> 00:05:31,439
Ah!

131
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,319
What are you doing?!

132
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,560
Let go, let go, let go!

133
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,120
Ow, ow, ow, ow!

134
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,360
What are you two doing?

135
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,759
Two grown men,

136
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,360
how would this look if word got out?

137
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:45,560
Guards!

138
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,800
Throw him out!

139
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,600
Prince!

140
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,319
Who is Jingjing?

141
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:49,879
Hold on.

142
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,839
You know where Jingjing is?

143
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,160
Jingjing is my only friend,

144
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,920
and the only person I've ever loved.

145
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,879
To pay for her schooling,

146
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,680
I founded Dudu Donkey Rides

147
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,800
and earned my first pot of gold.

148
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,560
In second grade,

149
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:15,879
she suddenly left without a word,

150
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:18,519
and never came back.

151
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,079
Do you know

152
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:25,319
how much I miss her?

153
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,839
I long to sing with her again

154
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,720
that happy children's song.

155
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,720
If you can bring Jingjing back to me,

156
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,879
I'll go back and be Emperor.

157
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,279
Since you two still have things to discuss,

158
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:51,000
I'll be on my way.

159
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,240
Ah, Prince!

160
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:00,959
Um...

161
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,160
Sorry to intrude.

162
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,240
Here's the thing,

163
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,040
you're quite busy,

164
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:04,680
so we...

165
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,839
So we'll definitely help you find Jingjing.

166
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,240
Prince,

167
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:10,879
what are Jingjing's distinguishing features?

168
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,399
Beautiful,

169
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,079
gentle,

170
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,319
and especially her eyebrows.

171
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,480
So gorgeous.

172
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,160
I'll never forget them.

173
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:27,959
Just like...

174
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,319
theirs.

175
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,199
Wow,

176
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,720
how unique!

177
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:39,639
Prince,

178
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,560
don't worry.

179
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,279
We'll definitely find Jingjing.

180
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,360
I'm counting on you.

181
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:46,800
You're welcome.

182
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,680
What's it got to do with me?

183
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,800
Search, search, search!

184
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,439
Go search, go search!

185
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:57,519
A student from twenty years ago?

186
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,800
Sorry,

187
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,920
I'm only eighteen.

188
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,240
I'm just here as a student teacher.

189
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:04,480
With such a common name,

190
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,879
we've got dozens in our grade.

191
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,879
I don't know which one you mean.

192
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,639
Eyebrows?

193
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,600
I can't see them.

194
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,519
In my class, students keep their heads down.

195
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,399
Can't even see their faces,

196
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:16,079
let alone their eyebrows.

197
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,560
Sir,

198
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:19,079
we'd like to ask about a student.

199
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,839
Ask away.

200
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,639
Young man,

201
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:24,560
I've been the handyman here for over fifty years.

202
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,439
I remember every single one of them.

203
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,920
Twenty years ago, was there a Jingjing here?

204
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,600
Do you remember?

205
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,399
This matter...

206
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:34,799
You two,

207
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:39,159
were you sent by Prince Mao to investigate?

208
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,399
Hmm.

209
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:46,320
Then no free consultations.

210
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,759
Since you work for Prince Mao,

211
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,600
The class from twenty years ago...

212
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,480
Let me think.

213
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:03,519
There was...

214
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,720
Xiao Ming,

215
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,120
Xiao Hong,

216
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,639
Xiao Hua,

217
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:12,159
Xiao Mao, Xiao Gang, Xiao Zhou, Situ,

218
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:18,039
Dugu, Xiao Chao, Da Fang, Da Dou, Er Mi, Yi Ding, De Hua...

219
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,600
Xiao...

220
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,399
Oh dear.

221
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,159
Nope.

222
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,039
There was no such student.

223
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,440
Are you messing with us?

224
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,720
He's hitting me!

225
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,559
Take me to the doctor!

226
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:36,840
Bullying an old man!

227
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,279
This is Jingjing.

228
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:41,840
Jingjing, huh.

229
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,679
She wasn't pretty at all.

230
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:47,120
She was top three ugliest in the school.

231
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,919
Back then,

232
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:51,120
she was expelled from school.

233
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:56,200
She used to get into fights all the time.

234
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,159
Her parents spent a fortune

235
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,240
to wipe her records from the school.

236
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,679
I heard later...

237
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,000
Oh.

238
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,759
Later, she ended up in a brothel.

239
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,600
A brothel?

240
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:09,960
Which one?

241
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,320
Come, come, come.

242
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,200
Ladies,

243
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,600
all of you, come in!

244
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,360
Come on.

245
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,120
Hurry, get in here!

246
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:15,600
Hey!

247
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,039
Hey!

248
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,200
Come on, ladies.

249
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,519
Greetings, young master.

250
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,960
Greetings, young master.

251
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,759
Young master,

252
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,320
all the girls you wanted are here.

253
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:26,279
Come.

254
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:27,080
Jingjing.

255
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,679
I'm the Jingjing you're looking for.

256
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:30,759
Elizabeth Jingjing.

257
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,279
The Prince's first love.

258
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,519
I'm the real Jingjing.

259
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,720
I am Jingjing.

260
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,200
I'm Jingjing, it's me!

261
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,639
I'm Jingjing! Me too!

262
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,399
Alright, alright, enough!

263
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:43,720
Young master,

264
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,399
this Jingjing you're looking for,

265
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,840
what's her family name?

266
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,200
What a blunder.

267
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,360
How did I forget the most crucial detail?

268
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,279
No wonder Prince Mao couldn't find her.

269
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,480
He probably doesn't even know himself.

270
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,559
No way.

271
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:04,799
I can't give up.

272
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,639
Just forget it.

273
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:08,440
We've been searching for a whole day and night.

274
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,279
Never seen someone make such a fuss over being emperor.

275
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,919
There are plenty of princes, just pick another one.

276
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,120
No.

277
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:18,039
I know everything.

278
00:11:19,759 --> 00:11:21,120
I Ching, tarot, astrology.

279
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,279
All for just two coins.

280
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,480
Hold on a moment.

281
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,440
That girl Jingjing

282
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:11,799
was once the top singer at Tianxiang House

283
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:13,799
But she only sold her art, not her body

284
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:15,559
Nobody knew her real name

285
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:18,279
We just knew her as Lady Shangguan

286
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,799
Then one day, suddenly,

287
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:22,519
Jingjing left Tianxiang House

288
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,440
She and Sister Hong

289
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,799
had a vicious falling-out

