514
00:22:13,319 --> 00:22:13,799
Jingjing.

515
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:15,839
Jingjing.

516
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,200
Jingjing.

517
00:22:19,839 --> 00:22:20,400
Jingjing.

518
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:21,000
Gouzi.

519
