Have a seat.

520
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,519
Gouzi.

521
00:22:30,079 --> 00:22:30,880
Just listen to me.

522
00:22:34,279 --> 00:22:34,839
My mother

523
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,160
