577
00:25:40,799 --> 00:25:42,039
That big idiot.

578
00:25:48,119 --> 00:25:49,440
Fate plays cruel tricks.

579
00:25:52,839 --> 00:25:53,319
Don't cry.

580
00:25:54,359 --> 00:25:55,119
Jingjing, no more crying.

581
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:55,799
There, there.

582
00:25:56,119 --> 00:25:58,119
This is a happy moment.

583
00:25:58,119 --> 00:25:59,000
Don't cry.

584
00:25:59,119 --> 00:25:59,880
We should be happy.

585
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:01,559
Get a hold of yourself.

586
00:26:05,079 --> 00:26:05,400
Jingjing,

587
00:26:06,799 --> 00:26:08,680
will you be my business partner?

588
00:26:11,759 --> 00:26:12,599
Gouzi,

589
00:26:14,839 --> 00:26:16,079
I will.

590
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:27,240
Prince,

591
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,359
no need to see me off any further.

592
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,920
Princess Ouyang, please wait.

593
00:26:36,799 --> 00:26:37,599
What is it?

594
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:39,839
Thank you for helping me,

595
00:26:40,279 --> 00:26:41,799
but I can't go back and be Emperor.

596
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:42,680
I'm sorry.

597
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:49,359
Prince,

598
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:51,640
do you truly not want to be Emperor?

599
00:26:52,799 --> 00:26:54,720
Business really does suit me best.

600
00:26:55,039 --> 00:26:56,640
And now I've found my best friend again.

601
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:58,319
Plus, I'm good-looking.

602
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,400
My life has no regrets left.

603
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:03,599
Let someone else be Emperor.

604
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:18,680
General Li.

605
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,519
Imperial Physician Xue is dead.

606
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,920
Who killed him?

607
00:27:25,039 --> 00:27:26,440
The real killer hasn't been found yet.

608
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:27,720
However,

609
00:27:28,559 --> 00:27:29,119
before he died,

610
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:31,240
he sent out a secret letter.

611
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:32,880
In it, he said

612
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:36,359
he'd uncovered the true cause of the Late Emperor's death.

613
00:27:37,279 --> 00:27:37,799
The Late Emperor

614
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,079
wasn't killed by rage.

615
00:27:40,079 --> 00:27:40,960
Then what?

616
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:42,000
A rare poison.

617
00:27:43,119 --> 00:27:43,920
What?
